### Get ProcessLogs
GET {{svc}}/ProcessLogs

### Add ProcessLogs
POST {{svc}}/addLogs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "logs": [{
    "record_ID": "9ce00211-387f-4d6c-85b6-6623ac89aa04",
    "type_code": 5,
    "message": "Message from HTTP file"
  }, {
    "record_ID": "9ce00211-387f-4d6c-85b6-6623ac89aa04",
    "type_code": 5,
    "message": "Message from HTTP file 2"
  }]
}

