### Update ProcessLogs (Always removes existing logs first, then inserts new ones)
POST {{svc}}/updateLogs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "logs": [{
    "record_ID": "05c60b6f-04e1-451c-b5d6-482be89f1f9e",
    "type_code": 1,
    "message": "Log Message after removing existing logs"
  }],
  "record_ID": "05c60b6f-04e1-451c-b5d6-482be89f1f9e"
}